No one would expect you not to resell it in the &quot;real&quot; world. $400 is  
a lot of money, as I know, since I paid it, too. You reselling it,  
even at a profit if the eBay market will bear, hardly constitutes  
filthy lucre in my book.

Just MHO. That&#39;s all.

Ann

